Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（會長拳頭處標誌捏自機動武鬥傳G高達中多蒙的King Of Heart(紅心之王)）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  還挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  輪到我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從手牌召喚三千院凪和綾崎颯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外伏下一張手牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家Attack！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等的就是你這招！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay召喚  高貴的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此處形象捏自少女革命）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣  桂雛菊的攻擊力就變成8500了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的攻擊還沒有結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也Cosplay召喚
